~ here we move A into B, dereference B to get the char
~ if the char is a null character we hop to the exit.
~ other wise we print the char, add one to our pointer in A
~ then hop back to the beginning of the loop 

$loop
    MVRR A B
    DREFR B B

    EQ 0 B
    LHOPT end

    PRINTR B
    ADD 1 A
    LHOP loop

$end
